Class CachedContent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.android.exoplayer2.upstream.cache.CachedContent

  • final class CachedContent
extends java.lang.Object

        public SimpleCacheSpan getSpan(long position)

      • getCachedBytes

        public long getCachedBytes(long position,
                           long length)
        Returns the length of the cached data block starting from the position to the block end up to length bytes. If the position isn't cached then -(the length of the gap to the next cached data up to length bytes) is returned.
        Parameters:
        position - The starting position of the data.
        length - The maximum length of the data to be returned.
        Returns:
        the length of the cached or not cached data block length.

      • touch

        public SimpleCacheSpan touch(SimpleCacheSpan cacheSpan)
                      throws Cache.CacheException
        Copies the given span with an updated last access time. Passed span becomes invalid after this call.
        Parameters:
        cacheSpan - Span to be copied and updated.
        Returns:
        a span with the updated last access time.
        Throws:
        Cache.CacheException - If renaming of the underlying span file failed.
